msgid ""
"[Commodore] Essential equipment for those late-night or early-morning "
"debugging sessions. Mainly used as sustenance for the hacker. Comes in many "
"decorator colors, such as Sausage, Pepperoni, and Garbage. See :ref:`ANSI-"
"standard-pizza`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Commodore] "
"深夜あるいは早朝のデバッグセッションに不可欠な装備。主にハッカーの糧として使われる。Sausage、Pepperoni、Garbageなど、多くの装飾的な色で来る。\\"
" :ref:`ANSI-standard-pizza`\\ を参照。"
